{
  "stem": "9963.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because I want you to know a piece of bread when you're hungry, no matter how little a piece of bread it is, that's life.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That is-- you know, when you're hungry, and you have something to put into your stomach, no matter how little it is, it is good to have it.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So whatever I could, I did, and I shared with my friends.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But that wasn't enough.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I start looking again.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And finally, [INAUDIBLE] on the kitchen that was over there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I went in.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was so gutsy that I went into the kitchen and went in to the manager from the kitchen, and I asked him if he can help me, because I want to help my friends that were hungry.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We came from a camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I told him the whole story.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And because I told him that I want to help my friends, but I didn't tell him that I want to help myself, he says, you know what will happen if a Gestapo man or SS man will come in the kitchen will find you, but you have no permission to be here.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I said, yes, I know what would happen, but I was so many times already in so many dangerous things, I take my chances.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "This is the only way I can survive.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he left.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He says, well, it not only will happen to you.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It will happen to me, too.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But it's worth to try it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he gave me a job to peel potatoes, to peel all of them and to clean and things like this.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I start working.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I always, you know, did more than they asked for.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I always was a very hard worker.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
